title: [Riddled With Runes]
description: Enclosed by paneled dark mahogany walls, the room features a bare silver-inlaid dark oak floor with an elaborate bronze brazier set in each corner.  Set flush into the rear wall, a faded ancient mural interrupts the flow of long marble shelves that sweep the perimeter of the room, the occasional wicker basket hung from below.  Aromatic smoke drifts lazily from each brazier, curling among the beams of the ceiling.
